title: Wagamama
typeOfFood: Japanese, Fast food, Juice bar, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Fusion, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. International franchise chain inspired by Japanese food. Vegetarian items are marked with a V and some are or can be made vegan. Reported the staff in this kitchen is cognizant about using separate utensils for cooking veg food, but likely has only 1 fryer for meat & veg. Has freshly squeezed juices, edamame, goma wakame salad, yasai gyoza (dumplings), yasai itame (tofu, veg & noodles in a coconut soup).
